{"word":"H7533 - רָצַץ - râtsats - raw-tsats' - Break","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָצַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râtsats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-tsats'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Break"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இடுக்கண் செய், பதறு, நகங்கு நொறுக்கு, நொறுக்கப்படு, நருக்கு, நடப்பது, நெரி, நெருக்கப்படு, உடை, ஒடிந்துபோ, ஒடுக்கு, கொடுரமாய் நடத்து, மோதிக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to crush, to oppress"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to crush, to get crushed, to be crushed"},{"paragraph":"2) to crush, to oppress (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"3) crushed (participle passive)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be crushed, to be broken"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to crush in pieces"},{"paragraph":"2) to grievously oppress (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"d) (Poel) to oppress (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hiphil) to crush"},{"paragraph":"f) (Hithpoel) to crush each other"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>crack</i> in pieces, literally or figuratively: - break, bruise, crush, discourage, oppress, struggle together."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4835 - מְרֻצָה - mᵉrutsâh - mer-oo-tsaw'/4835\">H4835</a>, <a href=\"#/H7518 - רַץ - rats - rats/7518\">H7518</a>, <a href=\"#/H7533 - רָצַץ - râtsats - raw-tsats'/7533\">H7533</a>"}]}